University of Virginia. University Photographer.
mdRecord.dcterms:description: The collection consists of photographs and negatives from the non-portrait file of Dave Skinner, the photographer for the University of Virginia Graphic Communications Services.

Topics include the visit of Queen Elizabeth II in 1976, graduation and other ceremonies, the Darden School Executive Program, athletics, concerts, conferences and institutes, speakers and entertainers, and new buildings.
The photographs and negatives are in sequence by file numbers 740001-770165.
